Gitorious Merge Request Monitor
- A simple service for following the status of Gitorious merge requests.

Currently supports reporting status over IRC.

Author: Jon Nordby
License: GPLv3+

== Dependencies ==
Python 2.x
Twisted
feedparser

== Usage ==
 $ export PYTHONPATH=./
 $ ./bin/gitorious-mrq-monitor https://gitorious.org/myproject.atom --irc-channel=#mychannel --irc-nick=mybot

